{"tid":881684,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"5日東京伊豆行程交通求評","createTime":"2018-10-29T15:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T16:55:06.000Z","uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fefa4bd443bb6fa06008f4fbcd81f3d79926abea","tid":881684,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"打算出年2月尾去睇河津櫻, 玩埋東伊豆<br />\n東京之前都去過, 所以今次重點係伊豆個邊, 同埋會有一日探下東京個frd<br />\n<br />\nday1: 下晝落機, 東京市內, 住淺草<br />\nday2: 探frd, 等佢帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday3: 東京市區出發去修善寺, 一碧湖, 住伊東<br />\nday4: 大室山, 仙人掌動物公園, 城ヶ崎海岸<br />\nday5: 河津櫻<br />\nday6: 返東京, 下晝5點機返香港<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家交通方面唔係太清楚, 淨係知有小田急伊東周遊券, 一係就3日東京廣域pass, 邊個好d?"},{"pid":"c4dd1ce4038ac9e1399b5aa6f978ca77ebed004f","tid":881684,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c408ef3d123a70ed577df34bcb4265cde4552ea4","tid":881684,"uid":140907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"伊豆個行程同我之前一樣咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f39b12b9552f8f12979b546fc2e57a01d6b0f17","tid":881684,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c408ef3d123a70ed577df34bcb4265cde4552ea4","tid":881684,"uid":140907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"伊豆個行程同我之前一樣咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講下你個時既交通點安排?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1c213bdfbfd2984291140b1264dc6cc1f358ba","tid":881684,"uid":11900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"有無睇岩邊間酒店，下星期去，乜都未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59399d41977baeac8f7d2aef3513c75f5775ce3","tid":881684,"uid":140907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f39b12b9552f8f12979b546fc2e57a01d6b0f17","tid":881684,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c408ef3d123a70ed577df34bcb4265cde4552ea4","tid":881684,"uid":140907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"伊豆個行程同我之前一樣咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講下你個時既交通點安排?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"個時我係三島入修善寺<br />\n所以我唔清楚東京有冇直車到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後修善寺坐架疏到仆街嘅巴士落伊東<br />\n好似兩粒幾鐘先一架去伊東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(果時冇去一碧湖 不過好似都要係伊東轉巴士上去)<br />\n伊東有巴士直到大室山<br />\n大室山又有架巴士去到伊豆海洋公園<br />\n果到有條路行十零分鐘去到城崎海岸<br />\n其餘就鐵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD4要預多啲時間<br />\n上次差啲去唔到城崎海岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}